。</p><p><br></p><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e55b5ea50eb7f5e63c2aa95a19f31afb_hd.jpg" data-caption="" data-rawwidth="2048" data-rawheight="2048" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e55b5ea50eb7f5e63c2aa95a19f31afb_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='2048'%20height='2048'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-rawwidth="2048" data-rawheight="2048" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="2048" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e55b5ea50eb7f5e63c2aa95a19f31afb_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e55b5ea50eb7f5e63c2aa95a19f31afb_hd.jpg"><p><br></p><p>很多人感叹减肥成功后的快乐、自由、成就感，但是我自己而言减肥成功的感觉应该就是：心有余悸。</p><p>因为这种心有余悸，</p><p>我再也不会因为嘴巴寂寞去吃零食了</p><p>喝咖啡只会选择美式或者冷萃</p><p>夏天很热会用冰水替代冰激淋</p><p>吃饭不饿了就停下筷子</p><p>等等等等</p><p><br></p><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-2fbf6c07b98d30febad8d9e1093b43fd_hd.jpg" data-caption="" data-rawwidth="2048" data-rawheight="2048" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2fbf6c07b98d30febad8d9e1093b43fd_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='2048'%20height='2048'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-rawwidth="2048" data-rawheight="2048" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="2048" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2fbf6c07b98d30febad8d9e1093b43fd_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-2fbf6c07b98d30febad8d9e1093b43fd_hd.jpg"><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>减肥真的很辛苦，再也不想胖了</p><p>我瘦了，看起来成功了，我自由了</p><p>但是，我真的自由了吗？</p><p><br></p><p>-----分割线-----</p><p>说我瘦了没有以前好看的，我不服啊！哼！</p><p><br></p><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f88b41c7571ac7152b48827cf88591a9_hd.jpg" data-caption="" data-rawwidth="2048" data-rawheight="2048" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f88b41c7571ac7152b48827cf88591a9_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='2048'%20height='2048'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-rawwidth="2048" data-rawheight="2048" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="2048" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f88b41c7571ac7152b48827cf88591a9_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f88b41c7571ac7152b48827cf88591a9_hd.jpg"><p>----分割线----</p><p>很多人问我怎么瘦下来的，个人认为我自己的方法不是很政治正确，所以就非常简单说一下</p><ol><li>没有运动</li><li>严格控制饮食：不会吃饱，只会吃到不饿</li><li>不吃零食、不吃甜食、10顿饭里大概有1-2次碳水</li><li>不暴饮暴食，遇到再爱吃的东西也参照第2条</li><li>喝水、喝茶、每天8-10杯</li><li>每天称体重，反思一下昨天有哪些行为导致体重变化</li></ol></span></div><div><div class="ContentItem-time"><a target="_blank" href="/question/26613082/answer/251913688"><span data-tooltip="发布于 昨天 19:28">编辑于 14:05</span></a></div></div><div class="ContentItem-actions RichContent-actions"><span><button class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--up" aria-label="赞同" type="button"><svg viewBox="0 0 20 18" class="Icon VoteButton-upIcon Icon--triangle" style="height:16px;width:9px;" width="9" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><title></title><g><path d="M0 15.243c0-.326.088-.533.236-.896l7.98-13.204C8.57.57 9.086 0 10 0s1.43.57 1.784 1.143l7.98 13.204c.15.363.236.57.236.896 0 1.386-.875 1.9-1.955 1.9H1.955c-1.08 0-1.955-.517-1.955-1.9z"/></g></svg>505</button><button class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--down" aria-label="反对" type="button"><svg viewBox="0 0 20 18" class="Icon VoteButton-downIcon Icon--triangle" style="height:16px;width:9px;" width="9" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><title></title><g><path d="M0 15.243c0-.326.088-.533.236-.896l7.98-13.204C8.57.57 9.086 0 10 0s1.43.57 1.784 1.143l7.98 13.204c.15.363.236.57.236.896 0 1.386-.875 1.9-1.955 1.9H1.955c-1.08 0-1.955-.517-1.955-1.9z"/></g></svg></button></span><button class="Button ContentItem-action Button--plain" type="button"><svg viewBox="0 0 18 18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="Icon Icon--comm